sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant App as SOMA App
  participant S as Supabase
  participant P as Partner
  participant N as Notification Service

  U->>App: Tap SOS
  App->>S: API: /sos/trigger (location, time)
  S->>S: Store SOS
  S->>P: Notify partner (push/email)
  S->>N: Send push notification
  N->>P: Deliver notification
  P->>App: Open app, view SOS
  App->>S: Fetch SOS status
  S->>App: Return status

  Note over U,App: If offline, app caches SOS and retries
  Note over S,P: (Planned) Escalate to authorities if no response